# thoroughfare

**Instance Property**

The street name at the place.

## Declaration

```swift
thoroughfare?: string;
```

## Discussion

For example, the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/SearchAutocompleteResult/thoroughfare] for the Golden Gate Park is `"John F Kennedy Dr"`.
